<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A sanctuary for <em>beauty & wellness</em></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="about-body">
          <p>Welcome to <strong>Nails For You</strong> — Richmond Hill's go-to destination for premium nail care and rejuvenating spa services. Nestled in the heart of the community, our studio offers a clean, modern, and warmly inviting environment where every visit is designed to help you unwind, refresh, and leave feeling beautifully confident.</p>
          <p>Our skilled team of certified nail technicians and spa specialists are passionate about delivering personalized, high-quality services tailored to your unique needs. From classic manicures to luxurious spa treatments, we bring artistry and care to every appointment.</p>
          <p>We believe that self-care is a necessity, not a luxury — and we're here to make it accessible, exceptional, and joyful for every guest who walks through our doors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">10+</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Years of Excellence</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
