<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Got Questions?</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked <em>Questions</em></h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Do I need an appointment, or do you accept walk-ins?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">We welcome both appointments and walk-ins. However, we strongly recommend booking in advance to secure your preferred time slot, especially on weekends. You can book online anytime through our website.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          How long do gel nails or acrylics typically last?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Gel nails generally last 2–3 weeks, while acrylics can last 3–4 weeks with proper care. We recommend scheduling a fill every 2–3 weeks to keep your nails looking fresh and beautiful.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          What is your cancellation policy?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">We kindly ask for at least 24 hours notice if you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment. Late cancellations or no-shows may be subject to a service fee to respect our team's time.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Do you offer services for children?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes! We offer child-friendly nail services for kids. Children under 12 must be accompanied by an adult. Please let us know when booking so we can prepare appropriately.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Are your products safe and non-toxic?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. We use high-quality, salon-grade products that meet safety standards. We carry a range of low-odour and vegan-friendly options. Please inform us of any allergies or sensitivities before your appointment.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          How do gift cards work?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Our gift cards are available for purchase online or in-studio in any denomination. They can be redeemed for any service and never expire. They make a wonderful gift for any occasion!</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          What payment methods do you accept?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">We accept all major credit and debit cards, cash, and gift cards. Contactless payment is available for your convenience.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Is there a service guarantee?
          <span class="arrow">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. If you experience any issues with your service, please contact us within 24 hours and schedule a follow-up within 7 days. We're happy to make it right. Please note that all services are non-refundable, but minor fixes are complimentary within this window.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

